addColumn

void addColumn(int column,
               AttributeDefinition attribute)
               throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Adds a new column to this attribute block. The new column must be represented by a single-field, multi-value attribute that is already defined for this block's object type, and is not used in any other block definition for this block's object type.

column - column number
attribute - attribute definition
